{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Under Fairy Hill</i> is a rouge-like bullet hell where you travel from room to room, trying to find the heart of the rogue fairy mound. Spacetime distorts inside it and it is teeming with strange creatures, hellbent on turning you into their dinner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Travel through dungeons, libraries, gardens, graveyards, casino's and more. Don't mind the flesh corridors though. Do not mind them. This fairy mound is completely normal and there's nothing suspicious going on here.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Creatures</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Many creatures roam the fairy mound. Enchanted tomes, eyeders, skeletons, candles, inklings, ghosts and glitches, all there to keep the fairy mound standing. But the fairy mound is not only populated with bloodthirsty creatures. Kinder beings have also taken up residence there and are often willing to help you, for a price.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228090/extras/description_image_1.gif?t=1735848499\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Weapons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What do you do with a sword? You throw it, of course! But you can also use many other weapons too, such as magic staffs or maybe even a magic 8-ball. The fairy mound is teeming with creative ways to eradicate your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228090/extras/description_image_0.png?t=1735848499\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2228090?t=1735848499","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2228090?t=1735848499","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228090/081bff539947